title: Can't click profile
body: So after a few games i notice that i can no longer check profiles i don't know if this happens to everyone but it is quite annoying as i want to see who i have close to mastery lvl 4-5 but i cant and the only way to fix it is re-logging. But after a few games after re-logging it happens again it really grinds my gears. That is all.

replies.body: new client coming in preseason. Hopefully fixes these issues
